## package

The `package` package has no real purpose. 

## Installation

Install `package` from Github with: 

```{r,eval=FALSE}
devtools::install_github("mdsumner/package")
```

## Example usage

What is this? 

```{r,eval=FALSE}
package()
```

What isn't this? 

```{r,eval=FALSE}
itsa()
```

No libraries were harmed in the making of this package.
